@startuml SequenceSync
title TIMELAPSE - Sequência: Sincronização Completa (UC001 - RF004, RF008)
actor User
participant UI
participant SyncEngine
participant RxDB
participant Plugin
participant DataSource

User -> UI: Solicita sincronizar
UI -> SyncEngine: sync()

SyncEngine -> SyncEngine: Pull primeiro

SyncEngine -> RxDB: getCheckpoint()
RxDB -> SyncEngine: checkpoint
SyncEngine -> Plugin: pull(checkpoint)
Plugin -> DataSource: GET issues?updated>checkpoint
DataSource -> Plugin: issues[]
Plugin -> Plugin: Map to internal
Plugin -> SyncEngine: tasks[], metadata[]

SyncEngine -> RxDB: upsert tasks, metadata
SyncEngine -> RxDB: saveCheckpoint()

SyncEngine -> SyncEngine: Push apontamentos
SyncEngine -> RxDB: getUnsyncedTimeEntries()
RxDB -> SyncEngine: timeEntries[]
loop cada timeEntry
    SyncEngine -> Plugin: push(timeEntry)
    Plugin -> DataSource: POST time_entries
    DataSource -> Plugin: 201 Created
    SyncEngine -> RxDB: update syncedAt
end

SyncEngine -> UI: syncComplete()
UI -> User: Sincronização concluída
@enduml
